text:
Ordered Kelp Knots & Duck Wings via Foodpanda delivery for $1.99 delivery and loved it so much! The food portion is just right for one person’s meal and the mala spice level is just right.

Just unbox and pour contents onto a plate, microwave for 1.5 minutes and you’re ready to go!
Personal favourite has gotta be the kelp.
I only eat their Chicken Wing Tips, love the sauce but wish it could be a little spicier. The rest of the items doesn't taste the same though it's supposed to be same sauce
Loved their mala mini lobsters. Hope they can have bigger sized versions. Please keep the promotion on going I bought 2 for $40.
